 order to better understand the meaning of the text within its manuscript matrix, why it was copied in the specific manuscripts it was, and how it was read and used by the different communities that preserved the manuscripts.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aChristian hagiographyxHistoryyTo 1500. 0aChristian saintsxCultzIcelandxHistoryyTo 1500. 0aChristian saintsxCultzNorwayxHistoryyTo 1500. 0aManuscripts, Old Norse. 0aSagasxHistory and criticism. 4aHagiografie. 4aJungfrau Maria. 4aManuskriptkultur. 4aMittelalter/Island. 4aPhilologie. 7aHISTORY / Medieval.2bisacsh  aHagiography, Medieval Iceland.  aManuscript culture.  aPhilology.  aVirgin Mary.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package English 2021z978311075072008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1z978311075070608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2021 Englishz978311075412408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2021z9783110753899oZDB-23-DKU0 cEPUBz97815015141280 cprintz978150151853940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150151414240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501514142423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501514142/original  a978-3-11-075070-6  DG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1b2021  a978-3-11-075072-0  DG Ebook Package English 2021b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075412-4  EBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2021 Englis